.H 2 "home"
This cookbook defined where certain directories are,
and some common uses of those directories,
relative to $HOME.
.H 3 "variables"
.VL 1i
.LI home
The current users' home directory.
.LI bin
The directory to place program binaries into.
.LI include
The directory to place include files into.
.LI lib
The directory to place libraries into.
.LI cc_include_flags
The [include] directory is appended to the search options.
.LI cc_link_flags
The [lib] directory is appended to the search options.
.LE
